				&kp Z &kp X &kp C &kp V &kp B &kp N &kp M &none &none &kp LEFT_META
				&sk LEFT_CONTROL &mo RAISE &mo LOWER &kp SPACE &kp RSHIFT &mod_alt_tap_dance
